=== Pronunciation ===
[[Category:Hebrew language]]
בּוּשׁ / bûsh / boosh
=== Etymology ===

A primitive root; 

=== Verb ===

properly to [[pale]], that is, by implication to be [[ashamed]]; also (by implication) to be disappointed, or delayed: - (be, make, bring to, cause, put to, with, a-) shame (-d), be (put to) confounded (-fusion), become dry, delay, be long.